&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;about the code block in org.apache.cassandra.cql3.Lists:362, there is an if/else if but there is no final else block to catch all other alternatives, is it intended&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It is intended. The only case left is when &lt;tt&gt;value == UNSET_BYTE_BUFFER&lt;/tt&gt; and in that case we want by definition do nothing.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
